She went through the forest.  She thought about what Wildfire had 
said, He's where your precios snake bot was.
She turned and headed for the cave.
"Blast that wolf.  I didn't go and run all over this blasted 
continant just to have him taken like that." She ran through the 
forest and soon came to the cave.  She looked inside and sniffed 
about. "Rowdy, You in here?" She stood at the entrance hoping he 
would answer her. But her instincts told her to fear the worst.
